# Button Component

## Description
Composant bouton versatile et accessible du Design System, conçu avec support multi-tailles (sm, md, lg) et variantes sémantiques. Intègre les tokens de spacing, typographie et couleurs pour une cohérence visuelle complète.

## Do & Don't
✅ **Do**
- Utiliser la variante `primary` pour les actions principales et `danger` pour les actions destructrices
- Adapter la taille au contexte (sm pour les actions secondaires, lg pour les CTAs critiques)

❌ **Don't**
- Mélanger plusieurs variantes dans une même zone d'actions
- Désactiver un bouton sans fournir une indication visuelle ou un tooltip explicatif

## 💻 Code interactif (Live Editor)

```jsx
const Button = ({ 
  variant = 'primary', 
  size = 'md', 
  disabled = false, 
  icon = null,
  children 
}) => {
  // Configuration des variantes de couleurs
  const variantConfig = {
    primary: {
      bg: 'var(--semantic-color-action-primary-bg-default)',
      text: 'var(--semantic-color-action-primary-text-default)',
      border: 'var(--semantic-color-action-primary-border-default)',
      bgHover: 'var(--semantic-color-action-primary-bg-hover)',
      textHover: 'var(--semantic-color-action-primary-text-hover)'
    },
    secondary: {
      bg: 'var(--semantic-color-action-secondary-bg-default)',
      text: 'var(--semantic-color-action-secondary-text-default)',
      border: 'var(--semantic-color-action-secondary-border-default)',
      bgHover: 'var(--semantic-color-action-secondary-bg-hover)',
      textHover: 'var(--semantic-color-action-secondary-text-hover)'
    },
    ghost: {
      bg: 'transparent',
      text: 'var(--semantic-color-action-ghost-text-default)',
      border: 'var(--semantic-color-action-ghost-border-default)',
      bgHover: 'var(--semantic-color-action-ghost-bg-hover)',
      textHover: 'var(--semantic-color-action-ghost-text-hover)'
    },
    danger: {
      bg: 'var(--semantic-color-action-danger-bg-default)',
      text: 'var(--semantic-color-action-danger-text-default)',
      border: 'var(--semantic-color-action-danger-border-default)',
      bgHover: 'var(--semantic-color-action-danger-bg-hover)',
      textHover: 'var(--semantic-color-action-danger-text-hover)'
    }
  };

  const config = variantConfig[variant];

  const styles = {
    backgroundColor: config.bg,
    color: config.text,
    borderColor: config.border,
    borderWidth: 'var(--component-button-borderWidth)',
    borderStyle: 'solid',
    borderRadius: 'var(--component-button-radius)',
    padding: `var(--component-button-size-${size}-paddingY) var(--component-button-size-${size}-paddingX)`,
    fontSize: `var(--component-button-size-${size}-fontSize)`,
    lineHeight: `var(--component-button-size-${size}-lineHeight)`,
    fontWeight: 'var(--component-button-fontWeight)',
    fontFamily: 'var(--component-button-fontFamily)',
    minHeight: `var(--component-button-size-${size}-minHeight)`,
    gap: `var(--component-button-size-${size}-gap)`,
    opacity: disabled ? 0.6 : 1,
    cursor: disabled ? 'not-allowed' : 'pointer',
    transition: 'var(--component-button-transition)',
    outline: 'none'
  };

  const iconSize = `var(--component-button-size-${size}-iconSize)`;

  return (
    <button 
      style={styles}
      disabled={disabled}
      className="flex items-center justify-center font-semibold transition-all hover:brightness-95 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 active:scale-95"
      onMouseEnter={(e) => {
        if (!disabled) {
          e.target.style.backgroundColor = config.bgHover;
          e.target.style.color = config.textHover;
        }
      }}
      onMouseLeave={(e) => {
        e.target.style.backgroundColor = config.bg;
        e.target.style.color = config.text;
      }}
    >
      {icon && <span style={{ width: iconSize, height: iconSize }}>{icon}</span>}
      {children}
    </button>
  );
};

// Rendu exhaustif
render(
  <div className="flex flex-col gap-12 p-8 bg-gray-50">

    {/* SECTION: Tailles */}
    <div className="flex flex-col gap-4">
      <div className="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest">Tailles</div>
      <div className="flex items-end gap-4 flex-wrap">
        <div className="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <span className="text-xs text-gray-500">Small (32px)</span>
          <Button size="sm" variant="primary">Sm Button</Button>
        </div>
        <div className="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <span className="text-xs text-gray-500">Medium (40px)</span>
          <Button size="md" variant="primary">Md Button</Button>
        </div>
        <div className="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <span className="text-xs text-gray-500">Large (48px)</span>
          <Button size="lg" variant="primary">Lg Button</Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* SECTION: Variantes (Primary) */}
    <div className="flex flex-col gap-4">
      <div className="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest">Variante Primary</div>
      <div className="flex items-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
        <Button size="md" variant="primary">Enabled</Button>
        <Button size="md" variant="primary" disabled>Disabled</Button>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* SECTION: Variantes (Secondary) */}
    <div className="flex flex-col gap-4">
      <div className="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest">Variante Secondary</div>
      <div className="flex items-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
        <Button size="md" variant="secondary">Enabled</Button>
        <Button size="md" variant="secondary" disabled>Disabled</Button>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* SECTION: Variantes (Ghost) */}
    <div className="flex flex-col gap-4">
      <div className="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest">Variante Ghost</div>
      <div className="flex items-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
        <Button size="md" variant="ghost">Enabled</Button>
        <Button size="md" variant="ghost" disabled>Disabled</Button>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* SECTION: Variantes (Danger) */}
    <div className="flex flex-col gap-4">
      <div className="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest">Variante Danger</div>
      <div className="flex items-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
        <Button size="md" variant="danger">Enabled</Button>
        <Button size="md" variant="danger" disabled>Disabled</Button>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* SECTION: Tous les états combinés */}
    <div className="flex flex-col gap-4 border-t pt-8">
      <div className="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest">Matrice Complète</div>
      <div className="grid grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        {['primary', 'secondary', 'ghost', 'danger'].map((variant) => (
          <div key={variant} className="flex flex-col gap-3">
            <span className="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 capitalize">{variant}</span>
            <div className="flex flex-col gap-2">
              <Button size="sm" variant={variant}>Sm</Button>
              <Button size="md" variant={variant}>Md</Button>
              <Button size="lg" variant={variant}>Lg</Button>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
);
```
